author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Mitsune performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 08, 2024. 

Songs:
00:04  Kokiriko Bushi
04:51  Soran Bushi
07:37  Roku-Go
11:06  Aizu Bandaisan

Petros Tzekos - Percussion, Vocals
Shiomi Kawaguchi - Shamisen, Vocals, Shinobue (Flute)
Youka Snell - Shamisen, Vocals
Daigo Nakai - Bass, Vocals
Audio & Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht
